item.description: If you haven't attended one of these FUN events, it's time you give it a try. Meet 8 (or more) singles of the opposite sex in a fun no-pressure environment, and if you don't meet someone you'd like to meet again, your next event is FREE. Go to www.8minuteDating.com to reserve your spot. Free appetizers, great atmosphere, great people. This will be the last 8minuteDating.com event before January. Join us in the Fun and you might have someone special to ring in the New Year! Happy Holidays everyone!!!
item.name: 8 Great Dates in One Fun Night!! Speed Dating in Manchester
